### How to download or install

You can download the repository as a zip from from this URL: <{{{url}}}/archive/master.zip>

Or you can install as an R package, {{{ package }}}, from GitHub with:

```{r gh-installation, eval = FALSE}
# install.packages("devtools")
remotes::install_github("{{{username}}}/{{{repo}}}")
```

If you install the package, run `build_project(<path>)` to recreate the project folder as an R project, then `run_analysis()` to re-run the analyses and produce the final report.

